Package: fda-recalls-dashboard
Title: FDA Device Recalls Dashboard
Version: 1.0.0
Description: A Shiny web application that queries the FDA openFDA API 
    for medical device recalls and displays them in an interactive dashboard
    with filtering, search, and visualizations.
Authors@R: person("Student", role = c("aut", "cre"))
